data.description: Seller will assist with closing costs. AFFORDABLE CLEARWATER HOME ~ PRIME LOCATION ~ PRIDE OF OWNERSHIP ~ ONE STORY ~ MOVE IN READY! Jackpot! This warm and welcoming unincorporated one-story home located in the heart of Clearwater is minutes from the #1 Beach in the Nation but not in a flood zone. The corner lot appeals to all with a manicured lawn and tropical landscaping that is filled with warmth starting with the teakwood tongue and groove ceiling of the covered porch and delightfully inviting travertine walkway to the "touch of blue" front door. Come in with a relaxed mind and find yourself enamored by the open floor plan of the 3 Bedroom, 2 bath oversized garage home that exudes a feeling of serenity & warmth. No exaggerations - take the tour - https://nodalview.com/s/1wyRJwd2v70vGGnAl4mkL3. You immediately walk into an "off mist" calm of the 1st living room ordained with plantation shutters which traverses to the family room and carries into the dining room and kitchen. Further along, you will come across the laundry room area which provides entry or exit to the backyard and garage. The fully fenced in backyard is massive with space for a pool or deck and spa - another area that is endless with opportunity. Plenty of parking on the other side of the fence off Temple Street. It is easy to see this would be a great home for those looking to stay. For my Investors, the house across the street sold for $590K and if you chose to turn the garage into a bedroom (as there is more than enough parking without it) your living area will be approx. 50sq ft smaller than that home. Best of all the 4-point and wind mitigation will be a no-brainer - Hip Roof 05/19/2020, Plumbing 12/10/2019, Heat / Air 10/2023 and electrical has a newer panel. This is a win as any Investor work would be by choice not need. Lastly, the house also works for pad -style or Air BNB as I mentioned earlier it is in unincorporated Clearwater. Current owners rent 2 of the rooms for 2K/month. This home is a precious treasure. Survey and Owner's Title Policy Available with Sale.
